languages.text: "Это ж что делается: хибары не жгут, блюстяки присмирели, за пайки на талон меньше дерут".
"What's even going on? They aren't setting fire to our hovels, them 'forcers have been muzzled, and now the rations are a whole card cheaper."

languages.original_text: "What's even going on? They aren't setting fire to our hovels, them 'forcers have been muzzled, and now the rations are a whole card cheaper."

languages.text: «¿Qué está pasando? Ya no nos están quemando las chabolas, los seguratas están atados en corto y ahora las raciones han bajado de precio una tarjeta».
languages.original_text: "What's even going on? They aren't setting fire to our hovels, them 'forcers have been muzzled, and now the rations are a whole card cheaper."

traits.locale_text: «¿Qué está pasando? Ya no nos están quemando las chabolas, los seguratas están atados en corto y ahora las raciones han bajado de precio una tarjeta».

languages.text: 「何が起きているんだ？彼らは俺達の小屋に火をつけもしないし、圧力は大人しいし、配給カードも全体的に安くなっている」
languages.original_text: "What's even going on? They aren't setting fire to our hovels, them 'forcers have been muzzled, and now the rations are a whole card cheaper."

traits.locale_text: 「何が起きているんだ？彼らは俺達の小屋に火をつけもしないし、圧力は大人しいし、配給カードも全体的に安くなっている」

languages.text: “这到底是怎么回事？那些执法者不再放火烧我们的屋子了，他们做事变规矩了，就连口粮都比以前便宜了整整一张卡。”
languages.original_text: "What's even going on? They aren't setting fire to our hovels, them 'forcers have been muzzled, and now the rations are a whole card cheaper."

traits.locale_text: “这到底是怎么回事？那些执法者不再放火烧我们的屋子了，他们做事变规矩了，就连口粮都比以前便宜了整整一张卡。”

languages.text: "Was geht hier überhaupt vor? Sie setzen unsere Hütten nicht in Brand, die Enforcer wurden zum Schweigen gebracht, und sind die Rationen auch noch eine ganze Karte billiger."
languages.original_text: "What's even going on? They aren't setting fire to our hovels, them 'forcers have been muzzled, and now the rations are a whole card cheaper."

languages.text: "Neler oluyor yahu? Barakalarımızı ateşe vermiyorlar, infazcıları susturdular. Şimdi de kumanyaları bir kart ucuzlatmışlar."
